summary: So, I watched a few Marvel videos (that didn’t even have anything to do with her) and suddenly youtube started recommending me...
body:
So, I watched a few Marvel videos (that didn’t even have anything to do with her) and suddenly youtube started recommending me all of this:

And… I’m sorry, but can someone tell me what’s going on here??? Has she actually done anything bad or problematic? Has she been rude to any of her co-stars? Is there some huge scandal that I’m missing out on? Or is this literally just some dudebros being offended that she’s not coddling their feelings and dares to be confident while female? 

Also honestly, so many of the Marvel actors are shitty people or have done shitty things. How is Brie Larson somehow worse than Chris “joins homophobic church that funds conversion therapy” Pratt, Mark “makes transphobic movies” Ruffalo, Scarlett “takes roles away from Asian actresses” Johansson, Paul “abuse apologist” Bettany or Gwyneth “scams people with fake medical products” Paltrow?

Brie Larson couldn’t “ruin Marvel” if she tried, because there’s honestly not that much left to ruin.
